{"id": "rios006", "name": "Audio_Academy_495_08_28", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Academy_1"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Katsuya, faster! You're too slow. Loser's gotta water the calendula.\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Wait a sec, we didn't agree to that before starting!\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Well... that's a new rule I just added!\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Nobody bullies their boyfriend like this!\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "So you better start running faster!\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Runnung_Grass", "Sprints"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Wah! Katsuya!\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "What's up?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Look! The flower didn't wither! Amazing! Unit 10 was right on point, as usual...\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "......?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Luckily, you helped protect me and this flower, otherwise there's no way it could have grown this much!\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Don't say it like that, it was nothing.\nRin, Unit 10... what's that? Doesn't sound like a person's name.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......!\nAhahaha... Did I say that?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Yeah, I just heard it.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "......\nRin, if you don't want to talk about it, then I won't ask.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move_02", "Holds Hand"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "I-I...\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Yeah?\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "If... If an Architect... was like a person, would you be friends with it?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Architects? Like people?\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Yeah, like if they had emotions and stuff. If they laughed, cried, got angry or sad, if they had things they liked...\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "... There's no way, right? I've never seen that type of Architect. It's kind of hard to answer...\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "But if it was possible?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "I...\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">Please, Katsuya...</font>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Uh... that... If it was a good Architect...\nI think... I'd try to be friends with them.\n\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "...! Really!?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Yeah, really... Where'd that come from?\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Katsuya, you promise you won't reveal my secret? This is important!\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Okay, I promise I won't tell anyone.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Unit 10 is actually... an Architect that's like a human, and she's my friend! Actually, it's related to the calendula situation...\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»Fast Forward»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "... That's how I met her. Whatta you think? Special, right?\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Wait, wait, wait. Rin, there's no way!? Best friend? Is she having a malfunction?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Definitely not! Katsuya, you don't believe me?\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "I believe you! But...\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Katsuya? Katsuya!\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Uh, sorry. I...\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "... \"I'm looking at the flower, not you!\" You're not gonna pull that crap again, are you?\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "... Damn! You making fun of me?\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Noooo. Heehee.\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Yes, you are!\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "Hugs"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Rin?\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "I just wanna hug, that's all!\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "... Oh. Okay.\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "... Um, Katsuya, Unit 10 is really different from other Architects. Let me introduce you to her, can I? She doesn't have any friends other than me. She's always alone...\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Katsuya? Can I, please?\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Okay, okay. Got it. A friend of Rin is a friend of mine.\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Academy_1"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也はやく！\nもーおっそい！\n負けた方がキンセンカに水やりね。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "は！？\nさっきまでそんなこと言ってなかっただろ！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "じゃー……今作ったルールって事で！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "お前彼氏に対してひどくねぇ！？\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "イヤならもっと速く走ってよね！\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Runnung_Grass", "走る"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "わっ！克也！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "どうした？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "見て！\nお花！枯れてない！\nすごい！10号機の言うとおりにしてよかった……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "それと、あの時克也が守ってくれたから。\n私だけじゃなくて、克也はこのお花も守ってくれたんだよ。\nあの時ボールにぶつかってたら、こんなに元気な姿は見られなかった！\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "やめろよ。照れるし……\n凛、今言ってた10号機って……なんだ？\n人の名前……じゃないよな？\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……！\nあははっ……あはははは～\n私……そんなこと言ったかな～\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "言ってた。\nしっかりと、この耳で聞いた。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "………\n凛、もし言いたくないなら無理には聞かないからいいよ。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move_02", "手を引く"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "あ、あのさ……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "ん？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "もし……もしだよ？\n人間みたいなアーキテクトがいたら……克也は友達になりたいって思う？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "アーキテクトが？人間みたい？\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "そう。\n私たちみたいに感情があって、笑うし、泣くし、怒るし、失敗を怖がるの。\nあとは好きなものがあったり……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……ありえないだろ？\nそんなアーキテクト見たことがない。\nだから答えられないな……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "もし……ありえたら？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "それは……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">おねがい、答えて。\n克也……</font>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "あー……そうだな……もしアーキテクトがいい奴なら……\n友達に……なってみたいかも、な？\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……！\n本当に！？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "うん、本当に……\nでも、急になんだよ？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也、これからいうことは絶対絶対ヒミツだよ。\nぜーったい他の人に話したらダメだからね？\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "うん、約束するよ。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "10号機は……人間みたいなアーキテクトなの。\n私の親友なんだ！\n私がキンセンカを育ててるのも、10号機と関係があってね……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……私と10号機は、こうやって知り合ったの。\nすごいでしょ？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "待って、凛。\nそんなことありえるはずがない！\nそれに親友って……もしかして、そのアーキテクトは故障してるんじゃないのか？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "そんなことない。\n克也、もしかして私が嘘をついてるって思ってるの？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "凛のことは信じてる！でも……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也？克也！\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "あ、ごめん……俺……\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……もしかして、まーた「お前じゃなくて花を見てるんだー！」とか言うつもり？\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……は、……っ！！\nおっ……ま、え～～～！俺のことバカにしてるだろ！\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "そんなことないよーん。あはは。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "そんなことある！\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "抱きしめる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "凛？\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "ちょっとギューってしたくなっただけ！\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……おう。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……ねぇ、克也。\n10号機は、本当に他のアーキテクトとは違うの。\n今度紹介するね？\nあの子には私しか友達がいないから、いつも一人ぼっちなんだ……\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也？ダメ？\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "ん、わかった。\n凛の友達は、俺の友達だ。\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Academy_1"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也，快一點！你跑好慢，輸的人要負責幫金盞花澆水喔。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "等一下，起跑前不是這樣說的！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "那……這是剛剛新增的規定！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "沒有人這樣欺負自己的男朋友吧！\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "所以要你跑快點啊！\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Runnung_Grass", "奔跑"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "哇！克也！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "怎麼了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "你看！花沒有枯萎呢！真神奇！聽十號機的話果然沒錯……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "幸好當時克也保護我，也保護了這朵花，不然它就不可能長那麼好了！\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "別這麼說啦，我會不好意思的。\n凜，你剛剛說十號機……那是什麼啊？聽起來不像是人的名字。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……！\n啊哈哈哈哈……我剛剛有講到這個詞嗎？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "有啊，我有聽到。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……。\n凜，妳如果不想講，我就不問了。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move_02", "拉手"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "那、那個……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "嗯？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "我問你喔……要是建造者……像人類一樣，你會願意和他們當朋友嗎？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "建造者？像人類一樣？\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "對，像我們一樣有感情。會笑、會哭、會生氣，會害怕犯錯，也有喜歡的東西……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……不可能吧？我沒看過這樣的建造者，有點難回答……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "如果有可能呢？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "這個……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">拜託了，克也……</font>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "呃……那……要是建造者很善良的話……\n我想……我會試著和他們做朋友吧。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……！真的嗎！？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "嗯，真的……為什麼突然問這個？\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也，接下來的話你能保證不說出去嗎？這很重要！\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "好，我保證不會說出去。\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "十號機其實……就是一台像人類的建造者，也是我最好的朋友！我會照顧金盞花也和她有關哦……\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……我跟她就是這樣認識的。怎麼樣，她很特別吧？\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "等等，凜，不太可能吧！？而且最好的朋友，這種事……她該不會是故障了？\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "才不是！克也，難道你不相信我嗎？\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "我相信妳！但……\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也？克也！\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "啊，抱歉，我是……\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……「我是在看花！不是在看妳啦！」，你該不會想要這麼說吧？\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……啊，可惡！妳在嘲笑我？\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "才沒有呢。嘻嘻。\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "明明就有！\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "擁抱"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "凜？\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "只是想抱一下而已！\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……好啦。\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……吶，克也，十號機真的跟其他建造者不一樣哦，我再把她介紹給你好嗎？她除了我以外沒有其他朋友，總是一個人……\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也？好不好嘛？\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "好、好。我知道了。凜的朋友就是我的朋友。\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Academy_1"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Katsuya! 더 빨리 뛰라고! 왜 이렇게 느려! 지는 사람이 카렌듈라한테 물 주는 거다!\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "잠깐! 뛰기 전엔 그런 말 없었잖아!\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "그건... 방금 막 새롭게 추가한 룰이지롱!\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "남자친구를 이런 식으로 괴롭히는 사람이 어딨냐!\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "싫으면 더 빨리 뛰든지!\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Runnung_Grass", "달린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "와! Katsuya!\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "왜 그래?\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "이것 봐! 꽃이 안 시들었어! 진짜 신기하다! 역시 10호기가 한 말이 사실이었어...\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "......?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "다행히도 그때 Katsuya가 공을 막아줘서 이 꽃을 지킬 수 있었거든. 안 그랬으면 이렇게 잘 크지 못했을 거야!\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "그런 말 말라니까. 미안해지게.\n Rin, 방금 말한 10호기인가 뭔가... 그게 뭐야? 사람 이름 같지는 않은데.\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......!\n 아, 아하하하....내가 방금 그런 말을 했었나?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "했어. 확실히 들었어.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "......\n Rin, 말하고 싶지 않으면 말 안 해도 돼. 나도 안 물어볼게.\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move_02", "손을 잡는다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "그, 그게...\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "응?\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "하나만 물어볼게... 만약에... 아키텍트가 인간과 거의 똑같다고 한다면... 넌 아키텍트와 친구가 될 수 있을 것 같아?\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "아키텍트? 인간이랑 똑같은 아키텍트?\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "응, 우리들처럼 감정도 있고, 웃을 줄도 알고\n 울기도 하고, 화를 내기도 하고, 실수를 두려워하기도, 하고 뭔가를 좋아하기도 하고...\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "...그럴 리가 없잖아? 그런 아키텍트는 아예 본 적이 없어서 뭐라고 대답해야 할지...\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "만약에 가능하다면?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "그건...\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">제발, Katsuya......</font>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "뭐...그게... 만약에 아키텍트가 착하다면 뭐....\n 사... 사귀어 볼 수는 있겠지.\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......!\n 정말!?\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "응. 정말... 그런데 왜 갑자기 그런 걸 물어보고 그래?\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Katsuya, 지금부터 하는 말, 꼭 비밀로 해주겠다고 약속할 수 있어? 진짜 중요한 얘기야!\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "알았어. 절대 아무한테도 말 안 할게.\n"}, {"id": 32, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "10호기는 사실... 인간과 비슷한 아키텍트이자... 나랑 가장 친한 친구이기도 해! 내가 카렌듈라를 돌보게 된 것도 10호기와 관련이 있어...\n"}, {"id": 33, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 34, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "...이렇게 10호기와 알고 지내게 된 거야. 어때? 확실히 일반 아키텍트와는 다르지 않아?\n"}, {"id": 35, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "잠깐, Rin!\n그런 게 가능할 리가 없잖아!? 게다가 가장 좋은 친구라니... 그... 그런 일은... 고장 난 거 아닐까?\n"}, {"id": 36, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "아니야! Katsuya, 설마 날 못 믿는 거야?\n"}, {"id": 37, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "당연히 널 믿지! 하지만...\n"}, {"id": 38, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 39, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Katsuya? Katsuya!\n"}, {"id": 40, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "아, 미안해. 나는...\n"}, {"id": 41, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "......\"꽃을 본 거라고! 널 본 게 아니라!\"\n 설마 이렇게 말하려는 건 아니지?\n"}, {"id": 42, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "....큭! 지금 나 비웃는 거야?\n"}, {"id": 43, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "그런 거 아닌데? 헤헤헤.\n"}, {"id": 44, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "분명 비웃었어!\n"}, {"id": 45, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move", "포옹한다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 46, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "Rin?\n"}, {"id": 47, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "그냥 안고 싶어서 이런 것뿐이야!\n"}, {"id": 48, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "...알았어.\n"}, {"id": 49, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "...저기, Katsuya. 10호기는 정말로 다른 아키텍트랑 다르거든? 내가 다시 제대로 소개해줄게. 아직 나 빼고 다른 친구를 사귀어보지 못 했거든. 항상 혼자서만...\n"}, {"id": 50, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 51, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "Katsuya? 싫은 거야?\n"}, {"id": 52, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "아, 알았다고. 알겠어. Rin의 친구는 내 친구이기도 한 셈이니까.\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Academy_1"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也，快一點！你跑好慢，輸的人要負責幫金盞花澆水喔。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "等一下，起跑前不是這樣說的！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "那……這是剛剛新增的規定！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "沒有人這樣欺負自己的男朋友吧！\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "所以要你跑快點啊！\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Runnung_Grass", "奔跑"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "哇！克也！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "怎麼了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "你看！花沒有枯萎呢！真神奇！聽十號機的話果然沒錯……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "幸好當時克也保護我，也保護了這朵花，不然它就不可能長那麼好了！\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "別這麼說啦，我會不好意思的。\n凜，你剛剛說十號機……那是什麼啊？聽起來不像是人的名字。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……！\n啊哈哈哈哈……我剛剛有講到這個詞嗎？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "有啊，我有聽到。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……。\n凜，妳如果不想講，我就不問了。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move_02", "拉手"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "那、那個……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "嗯？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "我問你喔……要是建造者……像人類一樣，你會願意和他們當朋友嗎？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "建造者？像人類一樣？\n"}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "對，像我們一樣有感情。會笑、會哭、會生氣，會害怕犯錯，也有喜歡的東西……\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……不可能吧？我沒看過這樣的建造者，有點難回答……\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "如果有可能呢？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "這個……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "<font size=\"1.6\">拜託了，克也……</font>\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "呃……那……要是建造者很善良的話……\n我想……我會試著和他們做朋友吧。\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……！真的嗎！？\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "co