"type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "好、好。我知道了。凜的朋友就是我的朋友。\n"}, {"id": 53, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>\n"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["Academy_1"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "克也，快一点！你跑好慢，输的人要负责帮金盏花浇水喔。\n"}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "等一下，起跑前不是这样说的！\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "那……这是刚刚新增的规定！\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "没有人这样欺负自己的男朋友吧！\n"}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "所以要你跑快点啊！\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Runnung_Grass", "奔跑"], "content": ""}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "哇！克也！\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "怎么了吗？\n"}, {"id": 9, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "你看！花没有枯萎呢！真神奇！听十号机的话果然没错……\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "幸好当时克也保护我，也保护了这朵花，不然它就不可能长那么好了！\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "别这么说啦，我会不好意思的。\n凛，你刚刚说十号机……那是什么啊？听起来不像是人的名字。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……！\n啊哈哈哈哈……我刚刚有讲到这个词吗？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "有啊，我有听到。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "……。\n凛，妳如果不想讲，我就不问了。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Body_Move_02", "拉手"], "content": ""}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "那、那个……\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Katsuya"], "content": "嗯？\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Rin"], "content": "我问你喔……要是建造者……像人类一样，你会愿意和他们当朋友吗？\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "conversation", "at